# Wittgenstein / NotebookLM manual-gated capture hygiene
# Raw provider transcripts must not be committed. Store only redacted transcripts,
# redaction reports, command metadata, and result manifests unless a future DEC
# explicitly promotes a sanitized fixture.
artifacts/manual-gated/notebooklm/**/transcript.*.raw.txt
artifacts/manual-gated/notebooklm/**/raw-provider-output.txt
artifacts/manual-gated/notebooklm/**/cookies*.txt
artifacts/manual-gated/notebooklm/**/storage_state.json
artifacts/manual-gated/notebooklm/**/.notebooklm/
